atic01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2365000/2368013/88779_600.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2365000%2F2368013%2F88779_600.png&h=00a87de6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://imoney.hket.com/article/2368013?fbclid=IwAR1T0mHWQYN1Tavkbr4Dat8ZpN3DWa-SklQBzdW4sYfzQ-i_CFX9Zgj_-UU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimoney.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2368013%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1T0mHWQYN1Tavkbr4Dat8ZpN3DWa-SklQBzdW4sYfzQ-i_CFX9Zgj_-UU&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67RmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=6555eb62\" target=\"_blank\">http://imoney.hket.com/article/2368013?fbclid=IwAR1T0mHWQYN1Tavkbr4Dat8ZpN3DWa-SklQBzdW4sYfzQ-i_CFX9Zgj_-UU</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">陳永堅</span>也指香港方面，現在<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人用煤氣已愈來愈少</span>，「以前一戶有3人，現在一戶只有2.5個人，人口少了，每個家庭簡單了，在家煮食要求又低了，洗澡會在家吃飯未必，好多人出街食，尤其住在納米樓的，<span style=\"color: red;\">基本上沒有廚房</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n他也坦言，<span style=\"color: red;\">煤氣跟電力的競爭很大</span>，「一條煤氣喉來到你家，入到廚房，是否代表你煮食會全用到煤氣？實際上並不如此，如你煲飯會用電飯煲，我相信有99%的香港人也用電飯煲煲飯，你煲湯很多時用電子瓦罉、壓力煲等，你早餐吃的多士也是用多士爐製作，也是用電的；以往用水煲煲水，現在大家也普遍改用電水煲，70年代後也出現了微波爐，其後也有電磁爐的出現，<span style=\"color: red;\">因此電力取了我們很多的市場</span>，電力跟我們有很大競爭。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一間公司既服務遲啲冇人用 我係你就沽貨啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3be4f86f905134f14024701f4f753efcb9d8a955","tid":1380014,"uid":110988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:28:18.000Z","msg":"公司常務董事話 :煤氣無人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac6b2c7b7f95d9b2ca1bc6f53740c11d4636ed4","tid":1380014,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:41:39.000Z","msg":"6月頭個價咪仲低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad1b85c632accf51a990b993e120f43147636f32","tid":1380014,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3be4f86f905134f14024701f4f753efcb9d8a955","tid":138